00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:21,240
derived from the principle of least action.

369
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:24,920
The principle of least action begins,

370
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:26,180
well,

371
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:26,940
first of all,

372
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:28,020
it begins with a picture.

373
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:30,160
As always,

374
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:32,240
we draw the time axis upward.

375
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,840
In the horizontal direction,

376
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:37,060
the horizontal direction stands,

