00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:59,450
is equal to one half

502
00:20:59,450 --> 00:21:01,620
a sum over all the particles,

503
00:21:03,020 --> 00:21:04,080
sum over I,

504
00:21:05,439 --> 00:21:07,480
particles labeled according to I,

505
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,260
one half

506
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:11,760
the mass of the ith particle

507
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:14,840
times Q sub I dot squared,

508
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:20,400
and then we would have minus the potential energy.

