00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,100
but in general,

520
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:49,040
it's just a potential energy

521
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:51,500
which depends on the positions of all the particles.

522
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:54,440
This is a simple example

523
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:56,720
