00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:31,440
don't move horizontally.

877
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,560
They move only vertically.

878
00:34:34,120 --> 00:34:35,520
That's a simplifying assumption,

879
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:37,480
but it's a pretty good assumption.

880
00:34:37,679 --> 00:34:38,639
It's much easier,

881
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:40,120
if you think about it for a minute,

882
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,560
it's much easier

883
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:43,719
to get the string vibrating vertically

884
00:34:44,259 --> 00:34:46,560
than it is to get it vibrating horizontally.

885
00:34:47,719 --> 00:34:48,159
It,

886
00:34:48,159 --> 00:34:48,540
uh,

887
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:49,360
typically,

888
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:51,020
the string is much stiffer

889
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:54,139
to get it moving horizontally

890
00:34:54,139 --> 00:34:55,159
than it is vertically.

891
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:55,980
So let's,

892
00:34:55,980 --> 00:34:56,040
uh,

893
00:34:56,040 --> 00:34:57,000
let's...

894
00:34:59,420 --> 00:35:00,300
Let's ignore

895
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,420
the horizontal motions

