899
00:35:05,940 --> 00:35:06,520
Now,

900
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:07,580
to get a handle on it,

901
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:10,980
let's begin by imagining

902
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:13,320
