906
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:20,880
which...

907
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:25,520
move vertically,

908
00:35:27,220 --> 00:35:28,420
but have springs.

909
00:35:28,600 --> 00:35:29,500
I'll draw the springs

910
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,700
