911
00:35:35,160 --> 00:35:37,140
Have springs connecting them.

912
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:43,120
In the limit

913
00:35:43,120 --> 00:35:46,440
that we take a continuously infinite collection

914
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:47,460
of mass points,

915
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:52,300
in the limit that we take

916
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:53,920
that continuous limit,

917
00:35:54,780 --> 00:35:57,620
this string becomes a field,

918
00:35:57,780 --> 00:35:59,920
or a mathematical model for a field.

919
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:02,100
It's not a field in real space,

920
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,580
but it has the property of a field.

921
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,640
It's a mathematical structure

922
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:06,920
of a field in a space

923
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:09,060
that exists between the post

924
00:36:09,060 --> 00:36:09,600
and the,

925
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:09,980
um,

926
00:36:09,980 --> 00:36:10,720
the peg

927
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,180
and the other end,

928
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:12,980
whatever it's called.

929
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,680
In other words,

930
00:36:15,780 --> 00:36:18,460
we can define a variable.

931
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:21,900
It's really just the height

932
00:36:22,980 --> 00:36:24,260
of the mass point.

933
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:25,380
Incidentally,

934
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:25,860
there's nothing

935
00:36:25,860 --> 00:36:27,000
to prevent mass points

936
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,400
from going lower here also.

937
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:32,240
We could call it y,

938
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:34,300
but I'm not going to call it y.

939
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:36,100
I'm going to call the height

940
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:37,300
of the ith point,

941
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,920
I'm going to label it phi,

942
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:40,240
whoops,

943
00:36:40,240 --> 00:36:41,440
phi sub i.

944
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:51,360
Phi sub i is simply the displacement

945
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,740
in the vertical direction

946
00:36:52,740 --> 00:36:54,480
of the ith mass point.

947
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:58,100
And I want to study the equations

948
00:36:58,100 --> 00:36:58,820
for this thing.

949
00:36:58,940 --> 00:37:00,140
We can get a pretty good idea.

950
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:01,060
We know what's going to happen.

951
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:02,740
Waves are going to go up and down.

952
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:03,780
When we take the limit,

953
00:37:03,860 --> 00:37:05,160
it's going to form a,

954
00:37:05,160 --> 00:37:05,780
um,

955
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,580
a mathematical string.

956
00:37:08,900 --> 00:37:10,560
The string is going to have waves

957
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:12,040
